{"tid":2513822,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"梁振英： 英政棍說中國違反中英聯合聲明，是否指中國對英國在香港的經濟利益還照顧得不夠？","createTime":"2021-05-03T00:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T03:38:41.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"62b1852433e4b67f8a3ed6d6931506108653b49e","tid":2513822,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:11:20.000Z","msg":"Such politicians as #LordAlton allege that China has breached the Sino-British Joint Declaration. But they have never been specific.  Never.<br />\n<br />\nLet&rsquo;s try to guess what they have in mind. <br />\n<br />\nArticle 3(9) of the Joint Declaration states, &ldquo; The Hong Kong Special Administrative Region may establish mutually beneficial economic relations with the United Kingdom and other countries, whose economic interests in Hong Kong will be given due regard.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nCould this be it? Are they saying they want their economic interests in Hong Kong to be given even more &ldquo;due regard&rdquo;?<br />\n<br />\n英國政客經常指中國政府違反《中英聯合聲明》，但從來沒有具體指出中國政府違反《聯合聲明》的那一條那一款。<br />\n<br />\n我們姑且臆度一下。《聯合聲明》的第三條第九款是這樣寫的，「香港特別行政區可同聯合王國和其他國家建立互利的經濟關係。聯合王國和其他國家在香港的經濟利益將得到照顧」。<br />\n<br />\n英國政客說中國政府違反《中英聯合聲明》，言下之意，是不是中國對英國在香港的經濟利益還照顧得不夠？"},{"pid":"d6a4b05638d6f53b8519489c621ff7ad2230198c","tid":2513822,"uid":24443,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:13:26.000Z","msg":"無人想理條傻西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9e420a151a5ea80816763b79a4ac6a1e89dc55","tid":2513822,"uid":36122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:15:49.000Z","msg":"先唔講佢既內容<br />\n一個前行政長官， 國家領導人日日係(外國既) 社交媒體發布d單單打打既言論， 對一個地方既形象真係好咩？"},{"pid":"de3669dfb48684b755371f2feff302859dac95b7","tid":2513822,"uid":2383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:15:55.000Z","msg":"下次quote 佢可唔可以加返個title （全家英藉）俾佢<img sr